reviewText: Cute movie for my 18 month old. We go camping alot and I thought she would really enjoy this movie and I was right!
By far the worst Barney produced. The costumes, the character voices and the kids age group where unlike any other episode my 3 year old has enjoyed before.
Good for baby so that's all that matters. Enough said on how I feel about it.
Barney is great fun and demonstrates learning at a camping setting.  A must have for young children!!

My 18 month old loves this video.  I find myself singing the songs to myself during the day.  It teaches kids to do their chores before they play and to clean up after themselves. They also have fun pitching tents, fishing and taking a nature hike.
